Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.10,0:00:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Oreki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.40,0:00:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, it's Chitanda speaking. Sorry for bothering you during the break.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.26,0:00:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you happen to have any plans for the day after tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.44,0:00:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.21,0:00:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.16,0:00:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Oreki...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.95,0:00:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that this is asking a lot of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.51,0:00:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but could you please carry the umbrella?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Carry... the umbrella?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.40,0:00:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.52,0:00:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.88,0:00:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I didn't explain it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.48,0:00:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is, we're having a Hina festival at the shrine near my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.43,0:00:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.95,0:00:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already April!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.87,0:00:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's held according to the lunar calendar.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.79,0:00:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, one of the umbrella holders for the dolls had an accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.07,0:00:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's no one else who can wear the costume.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.21,0:01:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the size should fit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.73,0:01:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a moment. Someone has to hold the umbrella?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.40,0:01:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.68,0:01:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you please help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.68,0:01:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.17,0:01:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.08,0:01:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.04,0:01:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have to stand there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.73,0:01:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you need to walk too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.98,0:01:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Walk? With a doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.81,0:01:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.71,0:01:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The dolls walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.53,0:01:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.38,0:01:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oreki!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.61,0:01:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you stop saying "dolls" all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.11,0:01:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bit embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.20,0:01:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.01,0:01:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, at the Mizunashi Shrine's living Hina festival, girls take on the dolls' roles.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.60,0:01:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.88,0:01:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I've played the Hina doll for a few years now.
