Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.67,0:01:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"Follow the little river upstream,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.08,0:01:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,then cross the Choukyuu bridge after the cherry trees."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:01:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{op}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.02,0:02:17.24,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(233,200}Today is a real mess, but I get over it with a sigh
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.82,0:02:20.32,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You get the idea, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:23.16,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}What do you wanna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.04,0:02:27.29,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You act as if nothing happened
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.29,0:02:30.62,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}As if your heart didn't ache
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.62,0:02:34.00,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It almost feels encouraging,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:36.55,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}the way you're rushing me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:39.78,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Hold it and let it overflow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.78,0:02:43.18,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}We're all imperfect
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:46.43,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I can't see it well in the light,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:52.52,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,350)}but if we can change our future selves
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:56.16,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Wake up and run
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.16,0:02:59.63,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Go and surpass the mirage
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.63,0:03:02.90,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Try to change and run
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.90,0:03:05.91,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}with the discomfort of freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:09.70,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}We can reach that shining light
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:13.15,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Follow it into the present
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.58,0:03:16.46,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Don't hesitate to act
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:21.68,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Deep or quick, just keep breathing
