Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, is that the cherry tree blooming out of season?{2 lines in audio}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Chitanda didn't know they were fixing the bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.39,0:03:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, can I cross?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.40,0:03:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll start work soon, and the bridge will be closed after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey{probably a name}, I've brought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, just put it down in the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.08,0:04:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.88,0:04:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Who're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Oreki. I've been asked to hold the umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't Chitanda tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She asked me to help out by holding the umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, instead of the Hazawa kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.60,0:04:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry. Just come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, who's taking care of the booze?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.19,0:04:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked Nakatake to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakatake, is it gonna be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, everything's going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.41,0:04:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about that thing during the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:04:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked the women to handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.64,0:05:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where are the lanterns?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,In the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.64,0:05:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I'll take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oreki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.19,0:05:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be holding the umbrella for the Chitanda girl, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.13,0:05:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr Hanai, phone call!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.65,0:05:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from the newspaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.32,0:05:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just can't get a moment's rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.04,0:05:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakatake!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the booze?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.36,0:05:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be here by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.62,0:05:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The procession gets back at half past twelve!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.08,0:05:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Does one pm sound like it'll be on time to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Make them hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.98,0:05:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.12,0:05:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,For crying out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.28,0:05:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the guy Chitanda asked to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.53,0:05:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. My name is Oreki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.02,0:05:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for asking you to come out all this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.08,0:05:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We're short on people, so we really need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.44,0:06:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd greatly appreciate your assistance today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to barge in as an outsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best not to get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.85,0:06:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's anything I can do to help, please let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.25,0:06:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}First time in my life anyone's told me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.42,0:06:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oreki, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Fukiya, have the worshippers' representatives arrived?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.26,0:06:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,All here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The children in the procession?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.59,0:06:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The living dolls?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.49,0:06:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.73,0:06:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanimoto, will the Choukyuu bridge be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.08,0:06:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked Mr. Murai to do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So we can get them to delay the work, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He told me to leave it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.38,0:06:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They've already started work on the Choukyuu bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.69,0:06:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.84,0:07:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanimoto, you made sure, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.65,0:07:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked Mr. Murai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.34,0:07:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oreki,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.67,0:07:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.32,0:07:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sono!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.64,0:07:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.67,0:07:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Take my truck and check.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.35,0:07:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanimoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.27,0:07:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Call Murai... No, call Nakagawa Construction.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.57,0:07:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This should do, right, Hanai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.85,0:07:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.17,0:07:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The procession is supposed to cross the Choukyuu bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you're not mistaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.55,0:07:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why are you staring at me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.79,0:07:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true! They've already begun work!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.62,0:07:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanimoto, what the hell have you been doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It doesn't make any sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:07:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Murai contacted the construction company!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.80,0:08:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He asked them to put the work off until tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why haven't they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.20,0:08:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone called them two days ago to say the work could go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't name themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.86,0:08:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.52,0:08:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got more important matters to deal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't we ask them to stop the work?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.49,0:08:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The TV crew's here already. What if there was an accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.83,0:08:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't they follow the same route back?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.96,0:08:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They could just walk down the east bank of the river then back the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The people on the east bank will appreciate that, but what about the west?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.51,0:08:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No doll parade for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.38,0:08:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about walking down to the Choukyuu bridge,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.88,0:08:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,doubling back, then doing the same on the other side?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't make the procession walk the whole distance twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.47,0:08:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what if we walk half way, then come back and do the same on the west side?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.97,0:08:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How could we do something so half-assed in front of the cameras?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:09:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what {\i1}can{\i0} we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.20,0:09:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we walk down to the Tooji bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.01,0:09:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If we go as far as the Tooji bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.68,0:09:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,then come back on the Kaya bridge,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.49,0:09:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll be just a bit longer than the original route.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.02,0:09:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tooji bridge, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.44,0:09:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, is Mr. Oreki here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, how can I help?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.52,0:09:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Chitanda's daughter is looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.36,0:09:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What does she want?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.72,0:09:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.76,0:09:34.38,signs,,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(0,0)\bord0\blur1\p1\c&HDCDCE6&}m 575 64 l 757 45 l 758 667 l 577 675 
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.76,0:09:34.38,signs,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fnArtificeSSK\fs75\blur0.6\c&H4B4F57&\frx4\fry354\frz4.297\org(911,415)\pos(644,334)}Living \Ndolls\N\N\N\N{\fs55\c&H2E3236&}Make-up\N and\N dressing\N room
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.45,0:09:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Oreki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for calling you this way, but I'm still in the middle of getting my make-up done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.89,0:09:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's Chitanda... isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.72,0:09:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I sent for you because I heard there was some trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.71,0:09:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.48,0:09:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.96,0:10:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The Choukyuu bridge...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So someone suggested a route that crossed the Tooji bridge instead,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.48,0:10:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but then everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.65,0:10:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But then everyone looked as though that was the worst option possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.80,0:10:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.08,0:10:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You've summed it up well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.84,0:10:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.83,0:10:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oreki, could I trouble you to deliver a message?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.75,0:10:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll talk to the priests leading the procession.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.31,0:10:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask my father to call the worshippers' representatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.70,0:10:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell them that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.85,0:10:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They should understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what she told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.62,0:10:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then, that's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, we're crossing the Tooji bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and get to work!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.98,0:11:12.02,eyecatch small,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.7\pos(271,167)}As the Sun crosses the middle of the heavens,\N the day and the night are equal.
