Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.56,0:11:12.02,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\fad(777,0)\blur5\c&H000000&\b1\t(0,400,\blur1)\pos(640,54)}Hyouka
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.44,0:11:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't you play this role?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.44,0:11:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The costume doesn't fit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.92,0:11:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.48,0:11:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This procession's a once-in-a-lifetime sight. I came all the way home just to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And I couldn't do that if I had to take part in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.07,0:11:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.76,0:11:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Done.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.34,0:11:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.56,0:11:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't really fit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.56,0:11:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I must agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:46.14,signs,,0,0,0,,{\c&H242522&\blur0.7\fnArtificeSSK\frz273.5\move(784,522,784,-37,29,3532)}The 62nd Kamiyama {\fs65}Living {\c&H302C29&}Doll {\c&H353432&}Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.20,0:12:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.36,0:12:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that... Irisu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.73,0:13:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.04,0:13:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is bad. This is really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I definitely shouldn't have come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.84,0:13:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My low-energy lifestyle is in mortal danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.60,0:14:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't see Chitanda...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.96,0:14:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't see Chitanda...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.43,0:14:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't stop thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.75,0:14:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't stop thinking about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.38,0:14:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What if I caught a glimpse of Chitanda's face,{up to sashi}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.06,0:14:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}taking in the makeup on her skin and her eyes, cast modestly downward...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.60,0:14:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Houtarou!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.83,0:14:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.92,0:14:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Chitanda and Irisu looked amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.34,0:14:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.38,0:14:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are they now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.54,0:14:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,In the main hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They're purging impurities.{gtfo kannagi}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.16,0:14:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.86,0:14:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, that outfit really didn't suit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.97,0:14:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.96,0:14:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You were such a waste for that role.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.31,0:14:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't recall asking for criticism.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.16,0:14:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go get another one of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.72,0:14:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oreki, thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.02,0:15:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,For what you did at Valentine's. I hadn't had an opportunity to thank you yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.12,0:15:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.70,0:15:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.70,0:15:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.04,0:15:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I blew my top too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.13,0:15:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost ended up punching him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.23,0:15:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Irisu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.66,0:15:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Oreki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You were one of the dolls, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.44,0:15:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a long story.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.44,0:15:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, I heard about the Choukyuu bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a bunch of things that don't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.16,0:15:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.16,0:15:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.57,0:15:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder. Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.93,0:15:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I hoped you'd be able to solve this mystery.{OH HELL NAW}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:15:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.24,0:15:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oreki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.08,0:15:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.09,0:15:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I played my part back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.78,0:16:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This time I'm just a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.82,0:16:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, you'll see only the real me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.93,0:16:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.40,0:16:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oreki...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.92,0:16:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oreki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.95,0:16:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Today was so hard! I had to put up with it the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, having to play a doll? Must've been tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.01,0:16:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The Choukyuu bridge! The incident with Nakagawa Construction!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.22,0:16:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.96,0:17:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to figure it out, but I was too preoccupied with my role for the procession.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.42,0:17:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wanted to ask you so much! I—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me guess. You can't stop thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.32,0:17:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly! You've noticed lots of clues, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.32,0:17:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a vague idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.79,0:17:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.06,0:17:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we write it all down and look at everything together?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.85,0:17:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, but what do we have to write on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.72,0:17:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready? One, two!
