Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.51,0:17:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Konari's son is brown-haired.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.85,0:17:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So we suspect the same guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Why did you think of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.32,0:17:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,First, we know for sure that someone called to tell them to go ahead with the bridge repairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.60,0:17:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So, who would have done that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.77,0:17:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone was in a rush today,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.67,0:17:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and only one person acted on the premise that the Choukyuu bridge would be closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:18:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And that would be Konari's son, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.73,0:18:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I talked to him when I was changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.62,0:18:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He said the procession was a "once-in-a-lifetime sight".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.24,0:18:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But that doesn't make sense. This festival is held every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not something a local would call "once-in-a-lifetime".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.04,0:18:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, that is a little strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.48,0:18:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But this year, it really was a once-in-a-lifetime sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.78,0:18:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.44,0:18:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The route was changed,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.80,0:18:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,so we had to cross the Tooji br—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, the cherry tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the cherry tree that was blooming out of season.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.66,0:18:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The only way you can see it is via today's route.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.75,0:18:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing the living dolls pass under a blooming cherry tree
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.94,0:18:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,really would be the sight of a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it all just for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wouldn't say "just".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.24,0:18:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oreki?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.22,0:18:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, why did you think it was him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.91,0:18:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He was the only one I could think of who'd be able to
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.79,0:19:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,keep his cool after causing so much trouble for so many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.09,0:19:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But after hearing your explanation, now I'm certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.29,0:19:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's his dream to become a photographer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.15,0:19:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He's attending a technical school in Osaka for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.84,0:19:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.78,0:19:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He must've wanted to take pictures of that rare sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.11,0:19:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.13,0:19:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oreki, I said in the dressing room that I was going to call the head priests, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.09,0:19:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and the chaos calmed down instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.82,0:19:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't much of a story, but please listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:20:09.56,signs,,0,0,0,,{\c&H6930C4&\blur1\fnFranKleinBold\b1\move(889,24,363,24,27,21632)}Do Not Cross
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:20:09.56,signs,,0,0,0,,{\c&H4C4366&\fscx85\fs20\blur1\fnFranKleinBold\b0\move(891,549,362,549,27,21632)}Nakagawa Constructions
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.68,0:19:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Long ago, this area was divided into the north and south.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.70,0:19:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Our village was to the north, and another village was to the south.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.42,0:20:09.56,signs,,0,0,0,,{\shad1\c&H312261&\blur1\fs25\b1\4c&H4A3682&\move(1325,372,980,372,24,14122)}Choukyuu\N Bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.29,0:19:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There were fights over land and water.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.64,0:20:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's long since past, but at religious events like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.87,0:20:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,crossing over into their land can still spark conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.45,0:20:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to give advance notice,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.79,0:20:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,but only a few people have the means to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where you come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If I let the people of the south know, we can pass through their land with no issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.84,0:20:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Satoshi was right to call your family powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.27,0:20:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This world is so tiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.34,0:20:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All I did was smooth over a problem{up to kamiyama no kita}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.02,0:20:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,between the north and south halves of a small town north of Kamiyama city.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.20,0:20:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I'm not saying what I did was totally insignificant,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.64,0:20:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't think it's anything major either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.48,0:20:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess... that might be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I go to college, I'll return here one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.09,0:20:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wherever I may roam{lolmetallica, lit "whatever path i may tread"}, I'll end up coming back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.98,0:21:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oreki, what did you decide to major in from second year onward?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.05,0:21:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I chose arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.50,0:21:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I chose science.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.52,0:21:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind coming back here, nor do I find it sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.64,0:21:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to fulfill my duty as the daughter of the Chitanda family.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.74,0:21:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking all this time of a means by which I could do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.27,0:21:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A means, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.65,0:21:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two that I can think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.67,0:21:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,One would be gaining wealth for everyone by producing high-value crops.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.68,0:21:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The other would be optimizing production by management so that no one will end up worse than they are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.98,0:21:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, I chose the former.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.44,0:21:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you chose science?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.14,0:21:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.96,0:21:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'd say the latter wouldn't really fit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.22,0:22:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,During the culture fair, I caused so much trouble for everyone that it made me realize.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.44,0:22:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm probably not fit for managing a company.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.91,0:22:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.81,0:22:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Please look, Oreki.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.31,0:22:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.61,0:22:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All we have is water and soil.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.62,0:22:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The people aren't getting any younger either.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.52,0:22:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think this place is the most beautiful ever,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.54,0:22:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,nor do I see that many possibilities here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.16,0:22:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.95,0:22:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to show it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.86,0:22:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.04,0:22:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That whole optimizing management idea you gave up on...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.83,0:22:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you leave that to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.32,0:23:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.84,0:23:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.26,0:23:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess this is how Satoshi felt back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.40,0:23:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gotten cold lately, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.72,0:23:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It's already spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.07,0:23:56.83,signs,,0,0,0,,{\shad1\c&H4E3E7C&\blur1.2\fs24\b1\4c&H4A3682&\move(1199,370,1319,370,29,2740)}Choukyuu\N Bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.07,0:23:56.83,signs,,0,0,0,,{\c&H885AE6&\blur1.2\fnFranKleinBold\b1\move(580,25,697,25,29,2740)}Do Not Cross
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.07,0:23:56.83,signs,,0,0,0,,{\c&H1F448F&\fscx85\fs20\blur1\fnFranKleinBold\b0\move(582,548,701,548,29,2740)}Nakagawa Constructions
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.23,0:24:28.94,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}The situation is unscientific
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.90,0:24:32.91,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,0)}A montage of emotions
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.91,0:24:35.49,ED,,0,0,0,,Who's calling who?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.49,0:24:39.70,ED,,0,0,0,,You look away when our eyes are about to meet
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.70,0:24:41.54,ED top,,0,0,0,,I can feel it
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.54,0:24:43.79,ED,,0,0,0,,Am I just imagining things? It's so cold of you
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.79,0:24:49.34,ED,,0,0,0,,It takes talent to read minds
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.34,0:24:50.51,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)}You know
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.21,0:24:51.84,ED top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You know
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.30,0:24:53.26,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I wanna know
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.05,0:24:54.89,ED top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.30,0:25:04.02,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}I'll fix the fire of youth in your heart while I can
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.10,0:25:05.86,ED top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}If we can do it today why leave it for tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.86,0:25:11.44,ED,,0,0,0,,I want to solve your mystery
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.44,0:25:16.74,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}Look for the back of the boy, burdened with secrets
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.16,0:25:17.83,ED top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Even today
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.12,0:25:22.41,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,0)}You are a fantasy and I'm drawn to you
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.41,0:25:26.58,ED,,0,0,0,,This growing curiosity
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.58,0:25:29.38,ED,,0,0,0,,There's no twist in the story
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.38,0:25:30.80,ED,,0,0,0,,I can't stop thinking about it
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.80,0:25:33.80,ED,,0,0,0,,It's so interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.80,0:25:36.34,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,350)}But why?
